div.p:
The WG focuses on the application and explication of existing standards, both
                onomasiological (TMF, TBX and SKOS) and semasiological (LMF, TEI, and Ontolex);
                draws upon the expertise of various DARIAH partners who are active in this field;
                and collaborates with relevant external projects and associations, such as the
                European Lexicographic Infrastructure (ELEXIS) and CLARIN in order to ascertain the
                widest possible reach of the Working Group’s results.
